item.title: CVE-2022-1814|2024-08-03T00:17:00.389Z -- unknown -- wp%20admin%20style
item.description: The WP Admin Style WordPress plugin through 0.1.2 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed
